{"tid":2322287,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"迪士尼怕玻璃心又碎 梁朝偉《尚氣》角色改名疑避辱華","createTime":"2020-12-12T08:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T22:23:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"05970f2dc097cc159549bb744b3eafa5bd1a8ffc","tid":2322287,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201212/QCM6LY4IHFFITO5WAIP6CG4ROM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201212%2FQCM6LY4IHFFITO5WAIP6CG4ROM%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jciTbLluyAJ10yBTn0YNn%2FPw%3D&h=6922a4ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201212%2FQCM6LY4IHFFITO5WAIP6CG4ROM%2F&h=9c57cd01\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201212/QCM6LY4IHFFITO5WAIP6CG4ROM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一連中伏多次的荷李活電影界，終於知道玻璃心並非浪得虛名。Marvel首部華人英雄電影《尚氣與十環幫傳奇》（Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings）昨日公佈了主要演員名單及所演角色，當中有梁朝偉、楊紫瓊、陳法拉等大家耳熟能詳的藝人，不過細心的網民發現，梁朝偉飾演的反派「滿大人」傅滿州，竟默默地改名成「Wenwu」（音譯：文武），疑似是為免玻璃心一碎再碎而作出的改動。<br />\n<br />\n反派角色滿大人（Mandarin），角色原名為Khan，是由「Marvel之父」Stan Lee及Don Heck共同創造，在1964年出版的第50期《Tales of Suspense》首次出現。角色初期常以清朝打扮亮相，且因為反派關係，滿大人主要財政來源自販毒及販賣白人奴隸，被視為在西方辱華觀念下，創造出來的角色，當中更出現了「黃禍」一詞。"},{"pid":"e784db1cbf401a563641af7159b233fb7f03365b","tid":2322287,"uid":17619,"like":84,"dislike":0,"score":84,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"叫Wuhan啦屌你老母<br />\n情節係放病毒搞鳩全世界"},{"pid":"f45315f10d53292358808be72ed335586d411258","tid":2322287,"uid":284432,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:11:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d19f4650e33edcd741a470c7ab4f57273133ef9a","tid":2322287,"uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T08:13:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3061715/org/6583f0b3994abe003cbaf018b0994d42.jpg/sc54lBBT4jjtWYNeFlWuxg2D